EXPLANATION
BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO TOWNS AND CITIES -- LOW AND MODERATE INCOME HOUSING
***
1 This act would require municipalities to report to the Rhode Island department of housing
2 regarding single-family low- or moderate-income housing available to rent or own which
3 information would then be made available to the public on the department's website and emailed
4 to interested parties who have provide their address or phone number to the department.
5 This act would take effect upon passage.
